settleCompetition


The formula for settling pool bets is "part * (turnover - commision)"
  
  Example:
  
        Alt A and B
        Peter placed 100 on A
        Pavel placed 300 on A
        I placed 200 on B
        A was the right alternative
        Peter get 0,25 * 600 = 150
        Pavel gets 0,75 * 600 = 450
        And I get mad
